      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk. it just feels like a lie to try and \"self care\" or whatever when everything is collapsing. it feels like we're just decorating our rooms while the house is on fire. honestly, it's getting harder and harder to justify even being here for it. it feels like there's no point in trying to survive a world that's already dead.",
