      "content": "yeah exactly. it's just all so heavy. sometimes i think the only way to actually find any peace is to just... not be part of it anymore. like, if the ship is sinking anyway, why stay on board and just suffer through the panic? it feels like the only way to actually take control of something is to just opt out before it all goes wrong.",
